    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Computer programs that serve a defined purpose, such as word processing or production of graphics, and that may be packaged and sold by a manufacturer.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
